Sentencas: Composite cathodes of (1-x wt%)Pr1.6Sr0.4NiO4+(x wt%)Y2O3-stabilized ZrO2 (YSZ; x = 0, 10, 20, 30, 40) abbreviated as Pr1.6Sr0.4NiO4+xYSZ, were prepared.
Titulo: Preparation and characteristics of Pr1.6Sr0.4NiO4+YSZ as composite cathode of solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The composite cathodes with x > 0 matched with electrolyte YSZ in thermal expansion coefficient (TEC) better than the cathode Pr1.6Sr0.4NiO4 did.
Titulo: Preparation and characteristics of Pr1.6Sr0.4NiO4+YSZ as composite cathode of solid oxide fuel cells
Preparation and characteristics of Pr1.6Sr0.4NiO4+YSZ as composite cathode of solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: +20YSZ exhibited the best performance on cathode overpotential and impedance.
Titulo: Preparation and characteristics of Pr1.6Sr0.4NiO4+YSZ as composite cathode of solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: When the cathode overpotential was 0.1 V, the polarization current density of Pr1.6Sr0.4NiO4+20YSZ was 0.28 A cm(-2), which is about 5.6 times higher than that of Pr1.6Sr0.4NiO4, 0.05 A cm(-2).
Titulo: Preparation and characteristics of Pr1.6Sr0.4NiO4+YSZ as composite cathode of solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The area-specific resistance (ASR) for Pr1.6Sr0.4NiO4+20YSZ was about 17.7% of that for Pr1.6Sr0.4NiO4 at 750 degrees C. Crown Copyright (C) 2009
